Yes.

60
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:32,440
我去召集行政委员会开个会  谢谢你
I shall summon the board at once. Thank you.

61
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:36,290
还有  牧师
Oh, and, reverend?

62
00:02:36,810 --> 00:02:38,770
