I want you there by my side.

117
00:06:28,130 --> 00:06:29,130
我不去
I will not.

118
00:06:30,470 --> 00:06:33,230
约翰·奥登是我的朋友  可能是我唯一的朋友
John Alden is my friend, perhaps my only one.

119
00:06:33,230 --> 00:06:34,260
你会让友情
And you would allow friendship

120
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:36,280
阻挡你自我提升的步伐吗
to stand in the way of your own elevation?

121
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,510
他是无辜的
He is innocent.

122
00:06:38,530 --> 00:06:39,720
你明明知道
And you know it.

123
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:40,490
我知道吗
Do I?

124
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:41,680
你又知道吗
Do you?

125
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:46,030
他就是你的酒肉朋友  突然你就能
A man shares your whiskey and suddenly you can...

126
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:48,190
就能看清他的灵魂
you can see into his very soul

127
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:52,280
证明他没被恶魔侵蚀走向黑暗了吗
and attest that it has not been blackened by the devil.

128
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:55,370
我可没有这番本事
I, myself, possess no such omniscience.

129
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:04,250
很久以前  我也面临过同样的困境
You know, long ago, I faced the same dilemma as you.

130
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:09,820
我要么跟一个我很喜欢的同学反目
It was state the case against a fellow student, a classmate,

131
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:12,430
一个我喜欢的年轻人
a young man I... I quite liked

132
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:16,640
要么缄口不语  放走一个被指控的巫师
or remain silent and allow an accused witch to walk free.

133
00:07:17,110 --> 00:07:18,140
让我猜猜
And let me guess.

134
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:21,230
你眼睁睁看着他被烧死了
You watched him burn.

135
00:07:21,230 --> 00:07:21,780
没有
No.

136
00:07:22,850 --> 00:07:27,270
我的情感打败了理智  那个年轻人被释放了
I let my feelings intercede, and the young man was freed.

137
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,760
可是两年后
And two years later,

138
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:32,490
他在一次邪教仪式上把两个处女割喉了
he slit the throats of two virgins in a satanic ritual.

139
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:34,280
都怪我
My mistake.

140
00:07:34,900 --> 00:07:36,880
