403
00:23:48,690 --> 00:23:50,350
"为了找梅西·路易丝"
...to find Mercy Lewis.

404
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:54,560
"穿过小河  在低垂的树枝旁  我发现了她"
"Past the lake, beside the weeping tree, I spied her."

405
00:23:54,850 --> 00:23:58,450
"穿过小河  在低垂的树枝旁  我发现了她"
Past the lake, beside the weeping tree, I spied her.

406
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:02,010
